body:
The following query returns movies that match the search criteria
and that are in the following buckets (years):

- 2000, inclusive lower bound for this bucket

- 2005, exclusive upper bound for the 2000 bucket and inclusive lower bound for this bucket

- 2010, exclusive upper bound for the 2005 bucket and inclusive lower bound for this bucket

- 2015, exclusive upper bound for the 2010 bucket and inclusive lower bound for this bucket

- 2020, exclusive upper bound for the 2015 bucket

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "facet": {
        "operator": {
          "queryString": {
            "defaultPath": "title",
            "query": "\"Marvel\" OR \"Avengers\" OR \"Iron Man\" OR \"Captain America\""
          }
        },
        "facets": {
          "yearFacet": {
            "type": "number",
            "path": "year",
            "boundaries": [1990, 2000, 2005, 2010, 2015, 2020 ]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$facet": {
      "docs": [
        { "$project":
          {
            "title": 1,
            "year": 1
          }
        }
      ],
      "meta": [
        {"$replaceWith": "$$SEARCH_META"},
        {"$limit": 1}
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "$set": {
      "meta": {
        "$arrayElemAt": ["$meta", 0]
      }
    }
  }
])
```

